<p><span style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 241, 214); font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">在班委的通力合作和全班同学的积极参与下，第28期入党积极分子学班顺利完成了新星计划的各项工作要求和目标，以新星计划总得分第一的成绩斩获“新星计划优秀学班”荣誉称号。学班在提高自身党性修养的同时，自觉响应总书记对新时代青年的要求，弘扬中华民族优秀传统美德，积极践行社会主义核心价值观。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 241, 214); font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;"><img src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/2n18Qa8gmELE0OZichV7JeZicFQMGA1A2MqH4n9mkIKAZuXjE1TBwXZqAJXpGX3c9r18Ie8fCqGXuKTEpic0NNJ7Q/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1" alt="图片" width="264" height="163" style="width: 264px; height: 163px;"/></span></p><p><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 241, 214); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><em style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">班长郭名滦：</em></span></strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 241, 214); text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">非常荣幸获得优秀学班干部的称号，首先要感谢组织的支持和学班各位同学的配合。在新星计划期间经管学班力致于建设学习型班级、完善制度建设，在学习中提高大家的思想觉悟和党性修养。在刚开始工作时，还模不着方向，经过这段时间的锻炼，我学到了很多东西，也成长了许多。在接下来我将继续努力，不断改进自己的工作方法，带领学班成员共同进步。</span></p><p><span style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 241, 214); font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;"><br/></span><br/></p>